{
  "info": {
    "name": "Medisalud API",
    "description": "Colección de prueba para la API de agendamiento de citas médicas.\n\nBase URL por defecto: http://localhost:8080\n\nRecomendado ejecutar en orden (o con el Collection Runner):\n1) Médicos > Crear médico (guarda doctorId)\n2) Pacientes > Crear paciente (guarda patientId)\n3) Citas > Reservar cita (guarda appointmentId)\n4) Citas > Consultar disponibilidad / Listar citas\n5) Citas > Reprogramar cita / Cancelar cita\n6) Validar errores > (casos que provocan 4xx a propósito)\n\nLas fechas de cita se calculan automáticamente (próximo día hábil 09:00/10:00 hora Colombia) en el pre-request de la colección.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('rand', String(Date.now()));",
          "const d = new Date(Date.now() + 7 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);",
          "while (d.getUTCDay() === 0 || d.getUTCDay() === 6) { d.setUTCDate(d.getUTCDate() + 1); }",
          "const y = d.getUTCFullYear();",
          "const m = String(d.getUTCMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');",
          "const day = String(d.getUTCDate()).padStart(2, '0');",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('slotDate', `${y}-${m}-${day}`);",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('appointmentDateTime', `${y}-${m}-${day}T14:00:00Z`);",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('rescheduleDateTime', `${y}-${m}-${day}T15:00:00Z`);",
          "const su = new Date(Date.now() + 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000);",
          "while (su.getUTCDay() !== 0) { su.setUTCDate(su.getUTCDate() + 1); }",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('sundayDateTime', `${su.getUTCFullYear()}-${String(su.getUTCMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0')}-${String(su.getUTCDate()).padStart(2,'0')}T14:00:00Z`);",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('outsideHoursDateTime', `${y}-${m}-${day}T23:00:00Z`);",
          "const off = 5 * 60 * 60000;",
          "const bnow = new Date(Date.now() - off);",
          "const dow = bnow.getUTCDay();",
          "const closing = dow === 6 ? 13 : 18;",
          "let mins = bnow.getUTCHours() * 60 + bnow.getUTCMinutes() + 4;",
          "mins = Math.ceil(mins / 30) * 30;",
          "const by = bnow.getUTCFullYear(), bmo = String(bnow.getUTCMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0'), bda = String(bnow.getUTCDate()).padStart(2,'0');",
          "const out = [];",
          "for (let mm2 = mins; out.length < 3 && (mm2 + 30) <= closing * 60; mm2 += 30) {",
          "  const h = Math.floor(mm2 / 60), mn = mm2 % 60;",
          "  if (dow !== 0 && h >= 8) { out.push(`${by}-${bmo}-${bda}T${String(h+5).padStart(2,'0')}:${String(mn).padStart(2,'0')}:00Z`); }",
          "}",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('penSlot1', out[0] || '');",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('penSlot2', out[1] || '');",
          "pm.collectionVariables.set('penSlot3', out[2] || '');"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "doctorId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "patientId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "appointmentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "rand", "value": "" },
    { "key": "slotDate", "value": "" },
    { "key": "appointmentDateTime", "value": "" },
    { "key": "rescheduleDateTime", "value": "" },
    { "key": "sundayDateTime", "value": "" },
    { "key": "outsideHoursDateTime", "value": "" },
    { "key": "errDoctorId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "errPatientA", "value": "" },
    { "key": "errPatientB", "value": "" },
    { "key": "errDocument", "value": "" },
    { "key": "penDoctorId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "penPatientId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "penApptId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "penSlot1", "value": "" },
    { "key": "penSlot2", "value": "" },
    { "key": "penSlot3", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Médicos",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear médico",
          "event": [
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": [
              "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('doctorId', pm.response.json().id);"
            ] } }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","doctors"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Dr. Gregory House\",\n  \"specialty\": \"Diagnostics\",\n  \"phone\": \"3001234567\",\n  \"email\": \"doctor_{{rand}}@clinic.com\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar médicos",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","doctors"] } }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener médico por id",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","doctors","{{doctorId}}"] } }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar médico",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","doctors","{{doctorId}}"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Dr. Gregory House\",\n  \"specialty\": \"Nephrology\",\n  \"phone\": \"3009998888\",\n  \"email\": \"doctor_{{rand}}@clinic.com\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar médico",
          "request": { "method": "DELETE", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","doctors","{{doctorId}}"] } }
        }
      ]
    },
